Package com.microsoft.azure.management.storage

This package contains the classes for StorageManagementClient.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StorageAccount
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure storage account.
    StorageAccount.DefinitionBlank
    A storage account definition allowing location to be set.
    StorageAccount.DefinitionCreatable
    A storage account definition with sufficient inputs to create a new storage account in the cloud, but exposing additional optional inputs to specify.
    StorageAccount.DefinitionCreatableWithAccessTier
    A storage account definition allowing access tier to be set.
    StorageAccount.Definitions
    Container interface for all the definitions that need to be implemented.
    StorageAccount.DefinitionWithGroup
    A storage account definition allowing resource group to be set.
    StorageAccount.Update
    The template for a storage account update operation, containing all the settings that can be modified.
    StorageAccount.UpdateWithAccessTier
    A blob storage account update allowing access tier to be specified.
    StorageAccount.UpdateWithCustomDomain
    A storageaccount update allowing to change the parameters.
    StorageAccount.UpdateWithEncryption
    A storage account update allowing encryption to be specified.
    StorageAccount.UpdateWithSku
    A storage account update allowing to change the parameters.
    StorageAccounts
    Entry point for storage accounts management API.
    Usage
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure storage resource usage info object.
    Usages
    Entry point for storage resource usage management API.

Package com.microsoft.azure.management.storage Description

This package contains the classes for StorageManagementClient. The Storage Management Client.
